=Rewrite these blocks to include images in column layouts:

**Original Blocks:**
{{ JSON.stringify($('Write Article1').first().json.message.content.blocks) }}

**Generated Images:**
{{ JSON.stringify($json.images) }}

For each image:
1. Identify the block to enhance (based on insertAfterBlock)
2. Convert it to a columns block with text on left (60% width) and image on right (40% width)
3. Use this structure:

{
  "id": "unique-id",
  "type": "columns",
  "order": X,
  "gap": "md",
  "columns": [
    {
      "id": "col-1",
      "width": 60,
      "blocks": [{ original text block }]
    },
    {
      "id": "col-2",
      "width": 40,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "img-block-id",
          "type": "image",
          "order": 0,
          "url": "image-url",
          "alt": "alt-text",
          "caption": "caption",
          "width": "full",
          "alignment": "center"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

Return the complete updated blocks array.

